snippet.title: Firefighters - Plant Fire Department
snippet.description:
Welcome to the factory fire defence! You and your colleagues will combat fire in an attempt to stop its destructive power. Solve seemingly impossible tasks, and use your equipment and special vehicles as you fight the flames. From small fires to structural fires to gas explosions, the factory fire defence has everything that a fire department faces at a modern industrial site.
Grow with the experience, become a pillar of support for your team and overcome all challenges – save lives!
